{"id":415092,"date":[{"year":1961,"month":2,"day":15}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"333","ytitle":"","mtitle":"春之颂歌","ftitle":"","authors":["邓初民"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"邓初民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"立春早过，大地回春，老病之躯，亦为春意所鼓舞，半夜不能成眠。倚枕构思，发为春之颂歌，以鸣盛世，工拙不计也。"}]}